Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:06.73,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yuki, you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:10.66,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Oh, Masachika-kun. Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.67,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,No problem. What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:14.90,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You could start with some pleasantries.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:18.10,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,How about, "Sorry, did you wait long?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.68,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sorry, did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:22.90,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yeah, you really kept me waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.90,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You two sure get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:27.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Didn't know you were here, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:31.01,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I sure am. Sorry for being the third wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.34,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Welp...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:34.97,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This jerk set me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:40.17,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So, you want me to help \Nsort out everything in storage?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:40.90,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:43.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.60,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Of course you'd be at home doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:47.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.90,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Could you help me out for a second here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:53.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hmm? Board games?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:57.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:59.12,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:01.53,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I see cards, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:04.00,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,We use these for school festival events.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:09.70,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I also happened to play during the new \Nstudent council's get-together the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:12.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh. Who won, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.88,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Um... I suppose I was technically the winner...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:18.64,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.10,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Less chatting, more working.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.50,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oops, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:24.14,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Pardon us, Alisa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:30.52,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Give me attention, too.
