Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:41.66,italicstop,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What is she thinking? Isn't that embarrassing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:46.02,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm throwing myself at him, and he has no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:56.17,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Come to me. Come to me.
