Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:58.68,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Great work, Masachika-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.96,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Thanks. You were a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:01.66,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:05.17,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,What, already done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:05.68,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.67,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun helped us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:11.44,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:14.03,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,I'm Kenzaki, the student council president.
