Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.28,top,TOYA,0,0,0,,I've heard lots about you and how talented you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:50.87,sign_generic,EPTITLE,0,0,0,,{\fs14\frz6.763\c&HFBE2FF&\3c&H974BEF&\b1\fade(1,450)\pos(365,317.364)}Episode 2
