Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:50.87,top,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:55.26,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, he definitely has an aura about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:58.08,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,No wonder he's our superstar president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:00.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.84,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.69,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad sending you off \Nempty-handed after all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.03,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Let me buy you dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It's fine. Appreciate the thought, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.07,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Why not accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.85,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You won't have dinner ready for you \Nwhen you get home, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:18.60,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.64,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,How do you know what he has going on at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:22.95,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,We go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.20,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:30.33,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Perfect, then. You two join us, \NSuou and Kujo Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.27,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Thank you for offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.56,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.09,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,It's not like a casual diner costs much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.28,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm impressed you finished so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:48.34,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,I was expecting it to take until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.66,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Masachika-kun's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:53.58,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,He can handle physical labor \Nand paperwork like it's nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.23,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,and he's an expert emcee and negotiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.09,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Quit hyping me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:01.13,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,It's not often Suou goes \Noverboard with the praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.49,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Kuze, any interest \Nin joining the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.37,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm done with \Nstudent council work forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.12,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I had enough in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:15.63,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Hmm. Being part of the student council \Nat our high school is certainly a lot of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.93,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,but it comes with its own benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.41,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,If I may be blunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.88,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,it'll have a massive effect \Non your recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hate to break it to you, \Nbut I'm not much of a go-getter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.87,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Come on, please join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.02,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Let's run for office together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:34.02,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Don't suggest that so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:39.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,And heck, do you even need me? \NYou're a shoo-in to be the next president anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.61,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,But I want to run the\Nstudent council with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nope! Can't be bothered!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:51.25,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,I must correct you, Kuze. \NSuou is far from being a shoo-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.10,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,We have other candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.52,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Chief among them is Kujo Junior over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:58.87,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:03.18,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll be running against \NSuou-san next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.39,Default,WAITRESS,0,0,0,,Here's your order!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.02,Default,ALL,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:13.94,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.87,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,Suou and I are going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.09,Default,TOYA,0,0,0,,You walk Kujo Junior home, Kuze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:18.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.41,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Okay, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:25.71,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It's fine. You don't need to walk me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You know that's not gonna fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:33.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:34.80,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.74,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Are you really gonna run\N for student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:41.05,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I am. I said as much earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.61,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'll be fine from here. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:51.51,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.43,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.54,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.89,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Did you walk Alya-san home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.15,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I'm staying here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.33,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,News to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.71,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It's breaking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:29.21,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\3c&HA095B7&\fnTimes New Roman\c&H1C263B&\b1}Teach Me How to {\c&H303793&}Love{\c&H1C263B&} 2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:26.08,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, an unknown hot guy \Nwalking with the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:29.21,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Gotta be her brother. \NOlder, from the looks of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.08,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Man, that should be obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:35.09,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Why won't the protag realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, you're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.18,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:41.89,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You're one to talk when you're pretending \Nto be my childhood friend in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.40,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What? It's not a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.02,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Do you even know what a childhood friend is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Someone you got along with growing up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.03,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.24,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,That includes siblings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:59.04,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,"Childhood friend," "otaku buddy," \Nand "sister" can all be true at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What a weird interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:05.67,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,More like a big-brain interpretation \Nof constantly evolving language!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.80,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Whoa, timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.27,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It really was the heroine's big bro with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Classic trope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.93,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,He's kissing the heroine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.28,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.96,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Damn, we're getting some wincest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.63,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:29.07,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Think about it. They've gotta be \Nstep-siblings or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.33,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:34.08,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It's only good when they're blood-related!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.95,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H333352&\fnTimes New Roman\blur1\3c&HC0C1CA&\bord1.5\pos(128,173)}Suou Yuki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.95,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H333352&\fnTimes New Roman\blur1\3c&HC0C1CA&\bord1.5\pos(520,168)}Masachika's actual\Nlittle sister
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Bwof!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:45.21,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Good morning, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.94,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It stopped being good a few seconds ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:53.34,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Come on, now. Your dearest little sister's \Nwaking you up with love and warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.09,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.81,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not letting you spin this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This is just DV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.67,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,DV? "Dear Venus"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:04.66,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Aw, big bro, you love me so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Domestic violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.41,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Fine, have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:15.70,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll hide under your bed \Nand grab your leg as you get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.38,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What are you even trying to be in life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.66,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeesh. Get off already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:21.98,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.70,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Getting a stiffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.36,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.48,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,All right, rise and shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.75,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You have a date with your dearest little sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:38.01,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\3c&HF3FFFC&\c&HC562D0&\pos(260,28)}Animated Movie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:38.01,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs15\i1\pos(409,27)\c&HACEBF0&\3c&H2B5F70&}Exciting Boogaloo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:38.01,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(339,137)\c&HEC9EF2&\3c&HFFFFF7&}Space Girl Chii
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:36.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.58,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:41.75,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,The movie-exclusive relationship moments \Nthat are never in the TV show...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.97,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.08,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Okay, time to rewatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, no! We're supposed to go shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:50.48,top,YUKI,0,0,0,,Unhand me! The movie is calling my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:50.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whoa! Quit lining up for tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:56.42,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I've been wanting a new summery dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:10:00.44,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,But I'm about to go broke buying merch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:03.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ouch! This is 15,000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:07.58,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Women's fashion costs a lot \Nfor every inch of fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.00,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,As an aside, sister of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.18,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What is it, beloved brother of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:18.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Is it just me who's been seeing a silver \Nsomething in the corner of my eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.26,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Not just you, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.01,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:27.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You've undone your ponytail and\Nswitched to prim-and-proper rich girl mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:32.18,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I noticed a long time before you did, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Really? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.05,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Pretty soon after we came down to this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That long ago? I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:44.96,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Hmph. I possess a hyper sixth sense \Nfor detecting the gaze of people I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:45.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Doesn't saying that make you cringe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.14,italics,YUKI,0,0,0,,I'm cringing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.64,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nothing to be smug about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.75,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Now, how do I solve this problem at hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.21,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,My, Alisa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.72,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sister of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Alya. What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.54,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, quite the coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:14.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I spotted you two a few moments ago, \Nbut I couldn't find the right time to say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.28,italicstop,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,"Few moments ago," my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.28,italics,YUKI,0,0,0,,"Few moments ago," my foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:20.00,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What brings you here, Alisa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.38,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, clothes shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.36,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Is that so? Have you had lunch already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.99,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:31.10,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,In that case, would you like to \Njoin us? We're about to—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hold up! Are you thinking of \Ntaking Alya to {\i1}that{\i0} restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.25,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:40.54,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You were looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It's clearly a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,We should go somewhere else \Nif we're taking Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What? What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.77,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Do you dislike spicy food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.65,Default,ALISA,0,0,0,,Spicy food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.23,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,1)\b1\3c&HCFE9F2&\c&H443DB6&\frx6\fry0\frz24.33\move(159,197,142,158)}Pon Curry\N Mild
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.02,Default,ALISA,0,0,0,,No, I don't particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.02,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\3c&HCFE9F2&\c&H443DB6&\pos(142,158)\frx6\fry0\frz24.33}Pon Curry\N Mild
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:59.54,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,We were about to go to a restaurant \Nthat serves spicy ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:02.53,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,If you don't dislike spicy food, join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.87,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Stop downplaying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.05,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya, let me be straight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.04,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It's not just spicy. That place \Nserves {\i1}super{\i0} spicy ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.91,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.88,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You don't have to come with us \Nif you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.09,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What, do you have \Na problem with my presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.17,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\fs25\b1\bord1.5\c&H212263&\3c&H828392&\frx18\fry48\pos(297,293)\frz324.9}Hell's \NCauldron
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:21.67,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnGeorgia\b1\fs16\c&H6D55DD&\3c&H1B1A3D&}Hell's Cauldron
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.83,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.25,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:28.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It's called Hell's Cauldron?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.10,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You said it's a ramen place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.31,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It very much is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:34.84,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Why does it have "hell" in the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:37.94,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Rest assured, it's in all \Nthe dishes' names, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.07,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.88,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Having second thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.57,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I simply needed a moment \Nto process how unique this place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.09,Default,WAITER,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:53.71,Default,WAITER,0,0,0,,Table for three? This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\c&HDCE6E7&\bord1\blur1\3c&H939495&\pos(354,71)\fs18\frz3.185}Hell's Cauldron
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\c&H3F39D3&\bord1\blur1\3c&H473A95&\fs13\frz3.185\pos(392,112)}Our trademark three stages of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\fnGeorgia\fs13\frx6\fry14\frz2.935\pos(380,151)\bord1\blur1\c&H3F2DB3&\3c&HB5BBBC&}Pool of\NBlood Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs11\bord0\fnGeorgia\frz3.694\pos(262,192)\c&HD6DADC&}Our most popular offering
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\fnGeorgia\fs13\frx6\fry14\bord1\blur1\c&H386C85&\3c&HB5BBBC&\pos(380,214)\frz3.816}Pincushion\NHell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs11\bord0\fnGeorgia\frz3.694\c&HD6DADC&\pos(249,259)}Piercing heat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\fnGeorgia\fs13\frx6\fry14\bord1\blur1\c&HB4B9B8&\3c&H000000&\pos(384,275)\shad1\4c&HC6CBF9&\frz4.521}Infinite Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs11\bord0\fnGeorgia\frz3.694\c&HD6DADC&\pos(282,321)}Makes even the demons of hell squirm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.59,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I have no idea what any of this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:03.60,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Pool of Blood Hell is a ramen \Nwith bright-red soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.77,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It has the least heat on this menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.48,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Pincushion Hell is so hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:11.22,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,it feels like your tongue is being \Npierced by countless needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.23,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What's this "Infinite Hell" at the bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.92,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's so spicy that your entire \Nmouth just goes completely numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.30,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I think I'll go with Pool of Blood Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:27.64,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Can't get too adventurous with your order \Nwhen it's your first time at a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:30.87,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,R-Right. It's good to start with the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.39,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Are you both ordering that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:37.82,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll have the same thing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.13,Default,WAITER,0,0,0,,Three Pools of Blood for Table 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:49.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You're dressed quite\Nboyishly today, Suou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.81,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It caught me by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:55.64,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It is a day off, so I went with this for \Na change of pace in my private time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:58.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah? "Private time," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:04.58,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,You see, I was in bed \Nwith Masachika-kun this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.80,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,In bed... with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:13.71,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yes. And because I wanted to wear \Nsomething different today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.85,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I asked him to let me borrow this shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.18,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.36,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, she just showed up at my place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,entered my room, and jumped \Nin my bed all by herself, believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Not buying it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.93,Default,WAITER,0,0,0,,Here's your order. \NThree Pools of Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.38,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:37.44,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Let's dig in before it gets soggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.19,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.06,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You okay there, Alya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.55,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.73,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, this is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:19.53,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Isn't it? The chilies accentuate \Nthe ingredients very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.44,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Help, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.71,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously, Alya, you don't have to \Npush yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.72,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I said it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.82,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, you said "it hurts."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.95,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.08,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:41.79,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.58,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,How do you like it, Alisa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.70,Default,ALISA,0,0,0,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:51.22,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,That's great. I'm so happy to hear that \Nyou enjoy super spicy food, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.54,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,At this restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:55.77,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,you can use this Devil's Tear seasoning \Nto make your food even spicier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.35,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Would you like to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.86,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She's doing this on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.34,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I think I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, Alya. You should really rethink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.86,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,One little drop won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.12,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You alive, Alya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.47,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Where's Suou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.77,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She ran off, saying she had something to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.38,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:51.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Want some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.48,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.00,Default,GIRL,0,0,0,,Mom, I want chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.36,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Say, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.56,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:13.63,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Why do you wanna be\Nstudent council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.51,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:20.89,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Do I really need a reason to aim higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Do you have a running mate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.68,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:31.28,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,But that won't be a problem. \NI don't need anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:36.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, that's not how it works. \NThe rules say you have to run as a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:41.12,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I just need a vice president on paper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.58,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'll try to find some \Nrandom person to support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.71,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.67,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}If only you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.63,flashback,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.95,flashback,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,Mom... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.85,flashback,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.87,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun, do you have any plans after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nah, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.72,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What about Suou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I mean, we could just meet up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:20.90,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Then come help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:25.22,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, you did say you wanted to shop for clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.37,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:36.78,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,A dude helping a girl pick out clothes? \NThat kinda implies a close relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:37.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.01,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:43.89,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya doesn't have friends \Nto go clothes shopping with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.02,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So she doesn't get how it all works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:49.34,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.34,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.22,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,We're friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:56.40,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Something about that \Ndoesn't sit right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.20,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:03.54,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Why'd he suddenly start being nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:08.04,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Wait, does he think I don't stand \Na chance of becoming president?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.42,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Stuff your pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.02,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go change! Tell me what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:16.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:20.93,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'll blow his mind with my fashion show \Nand show him who's boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:27.93,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Wait a second. He might hear me \Nchanging outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.21,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun! Move farther away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:32.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.12,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yes, I look nice, if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:53.83,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:58.28,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What if he doesn't react?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.46,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.60,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hmph! Try it, \Nand I'll slap your mouth off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:10.89,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.05,Default,STAFF,0,0,0,,Wow, so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, you look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.81,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That outfit ups your elegance and femininity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:22.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,and makes you look even prettier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:24.75,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:25.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.21,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:30.70,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.79,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,He praised the heck out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.29,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't handle this embarrassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.71,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,How does she do this all the time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.14,Default,CUSTOMER1,0,0,0,,Teenage couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.67,Default,CUSTOMER2,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.14,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,He said I was pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.93,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,He said I was pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.88,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I didn't know he had it in him \Nto compliment a girl right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:56.98,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.48,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,He's kind of... used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:06.80,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Her outfit today was pretty boyish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:09.84,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What do you say about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:14.19,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Now you look really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:19.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You're more hot than cute, \Nso I think it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:21.38,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,O-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.96,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You think? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.81,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wow, that's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sexy suits you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:32.77,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.02,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:35.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You're so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:41.52,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\an7\c&HD08DEF&\3c&HFCFDFF&\fs23}Pretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:41.52,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\an9\c&HD08DEF&\3c&HFCFDFF&\fs23}Pretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty\N\NPretty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:40.28,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,Wow, this feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.31,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.03,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:52.13,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,This may be a little too revealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:55.05,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,But I'm sure Kuze-kun will like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.91,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.61,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Wow, Alisa-san, you're so daring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:10.68,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:20.23,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}I wanna disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.58,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:24.31,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She wants to disappear, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:27.42,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Hah, what a big baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:28.43,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Who're you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:40.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,See you Monday, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.42,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Today was fun. We should hang out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:46.57,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah, we should. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:55.87,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What was I thinking with that skimpy skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.75,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,They must think I'm a skank!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:04.56,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Wait, why'd they get off at the same station?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:05.94,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:06.94,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:08.73,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?!
